description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Sleep Meditation Guided 20 Minute' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let this Original 20 minute guided meditation for sleep, recorded by us to put you into a deeply relaxing state so that you can drift away for the night.  This meditation will induce sleep by scanning each of your body parts, allowing them to let go of any tension, while becoming very relaxed, allowing gravity to do it's thing.  Have a good night :)  Enjoy!

Spoken Voice: Original Commentary recorded by us.
Background Music: Exclusively owned and produced by us (Great Meditation).
Background Image: is an original derivative unique to this channel, Transformed from Licensed images where attributions are not required....
